high_descs: turn around and cross the room to the counter between the stove and the sink
take the spoon from the counter
turn around and move forward slightly. Stop when you are next to the coffee maker, and turn to face it.
put the spoon in the mug on the counter
take the mug with the spoon in it
return to the corner between the sink and the stove. Turn to face the sink
place the mug in the right-hand sink
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a spoon in it in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter with the spoon on it to the right of the stove.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Turn right and walk to the counter above the dishwasher.
Place the spoon in the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a spoon in it into the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the counter in between the sink and stove.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Turn right and face the coffee maker on the counter.
Place the spoon in the black cup in front of the coffee maker.
Pick up the cup with the spoon.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Place the cup with the spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a black cup with the spoon in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the right of the black stove.
Pick up the spoon from the back of the counter.
Turn around and hang a left to reach the blue coffee maker.
Place the spoon inside the black mug in front of the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug with the spoon inside from the counter top.
Walk to the sink to the left of the coffee maker near the window.
Place the mug with the spoon inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a spoon in a sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the counter to the right of the stove top.
Take the spoon from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn left to the dishwasher, go to the dishwasher.
Put the spoon in the gray cup in front of the coffee maker on the counter above the dishwasher.
Take the cup from the counter.
Turn left, go straight to the counter to the right of the stove top, turn right to face the sink.
Put the cup in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a spoon in it in a sink.
